                     <interp inst="t18450303-778-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>stealing one watch, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 pair of earrings, 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 brooch, 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 pencil-case, 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18450303-name-823" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450303-name-823" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
